### Description of Issue

[This merged PR](https://github.com/saltstack/salt/pull/41210) clashes with the downloadonly parameter we already had for the [yum](https://github.com/Da-Juan/salt/blob/ed8dde469a34b00532b0e0eafa57d1de6fb00aa4/salt/modules/yumpkg.py#L1113) and [zypper](https://github.com/Da-Juan/salt/blob/ed8dde469a34b00532b0e0eafa57d1de6fb00aa4/salt/modules/zypper.py#L898) module. The parameter should be `downloadonly` and not `download_only`.

### Versions Report
Salt >= 2017.7.0.
